{"tha-ap499:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap499:0.2":"Kinkanipupphavagga ","tha-ap499:0.3":"Udakadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap499:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap499:1.2":"bhikkhusanghe anuttare; ","tha-ap499:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap499:1.4":"panighatamapurayim. ","tha-ap499:2.1":"Pabbatagge dumagge va, ","tha-ap499:2.2":"akase vatha bhumiyam; ","tha-ap499:2.3":"Yada paniyamicchami, ","tha-ap499:2.4":"khippam nibbattate mama. ","tha-ap499:3.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap499:3.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap499:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap499:3.4":"dakadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap499:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap499:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap499:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap499:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap499:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap499:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap499:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap499:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap499:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap499:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma udakadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap499:8.1":"Udakadayakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}